pull_request.title: Configurable dvalin-jaxrs
pull_request.body:
Make dvalin-jaxrs more configurable:

* Only start jetty if new http spring profile is active to enable client-only services
* Move ApiListing and swagger-ui into separate module to make it optional and reduce size of services which don't need it
* Update swagger-ui

pull_request.body: This PR adds [testcontainers](https://github.com/testcontainers/testcontainers-java)  to run JUnit tests against a CUPS Docker container. Running integration tests no longer depends on local CUPS instance - works on Windows and GitHub Action builds as well.
